{"tid":746901,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"點先搵到合適嘅髮型？","createTime":"2018-07-18T03:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T05:23:04.000Z","uid":82694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2d0f90bd2b675d227fc122c1c674aed13a1566d5","tid":746901,"uid":82694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:14:49.000Z","msg":"每次去剪髮都只係可以講「照舊」，「修短啲」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早幾日係ig見到有個日本仔會幫啲毒撚執到變勁撚型 （或者順眼番好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n想知香港有冇髮型屋都係有設計師幫你搵個最適合嘅髮型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648bb212c20f895995fa5ea2f003417429b2ee3a","tid":746901,"uid":117947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:20:27.000Z","msg":"係囉, 我次次都係話修短少少就算<br />\n好驚俾人剪到好樣衰"},{"pid":"6c5096d97ec58d12202fff6534bd63440350ec2b","tid":746901,"uid":10895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:26:29.000Z","msg":"想電髮又驚柒"},{"pid":"ff9ecb9e2dd1ee7b8757b8a9859ee43c67f7df96","tid":746901,"uid":125460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:26:32.000Z","msg":"同求🙇🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"d03ddcc0ecc7f826dc7fcbdc46e48666b8d315b4","tid":746901,"uid":21355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:31:26.000Z","msg":"搵啲貴啲嘅同佢講你話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb98515c2836aa2c6473c6dea3fecd4e6723719","tid":746901,"uid":82694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:41:34.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打係成功案例可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33782ab6f693ba0529a8c282145